title: Bug 121687: Exception thrown when exporting data in a table inside a grid cell
OB: When trying to export data in a table that is inside a grid cell, an exception is thrown.
EB: The data in the table inside the grid cell should be exported successfully without any exceptions being thrown.
SR: To reproduce the issue: 1. Insert a grid. 2. Insert one table into one grid cell. 3. Insert another table into the other grid cell.
